 some time, most will agree that they are the best earbuds you can buy. While they work great with all devices, you\u0026#39;re going to get the best experience if you pair them with Apple products. \u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eThese earbuds not only deliver excellent sound, but they also have fantastic ANC capabilities as well. Furthermore, you also get audio perks like spatial audio, which can take your content to another level. And the AirPods can even be used as hearing devices too. \u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eIn addition to the above, you also get up to six hours of use per charge, and the charging case can provide up to 30 hours total. The great thing about this recent model is that you can charge the case using USB-C. Of course, wireless charging is also an option as well. \u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eDespite their small size, the AirPods Pro are quite durable, providing excellent protection against moisture and dust. For the most part, you really can\u0026#39;t beat these earbuds as they provide the complete package. Again, they work with all devices, but are best with Apple\u0026#39;s own products. \u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eGrab these AirPods Pro for less while you can. The discount is something worth considering, especially if you\u0026#39;ve been holding out to buy a new pair of earbuds. \u003c/p\u003e    \u003c/div\u003e\n    \n                \n        \n        \n\n\n        \n\n\n\n\n\n                    \n        \n    \u003c/article\u003e\n\n    \n            \n        \u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
